Blocks.childText: 29 God will take Care of You. -Concluded. Fa - ther, Re - deem er and Friend! Je - sus will an - swer when- ev er you call, He will take care of you, trust Him for all. HOLY GHOST, WITH LIGHT DIVINE. MY FAITH LOOKS UP TO THEE. Pleyels Hymn-Key G. Tune Olivet-Key E2. Holy Ghost, with light divine, My faith looks up to thee, Thou Lamb of Calvary, Shine upon this heart of mine; Saviour divine: Chase the shades of night away, Now hear me while I pray, Turn my darkness into day. Take all my guilt away, o let me from this day Holy Ghost, with power divine, Be wholly thine! Cleanse this guilty heart of mine; May thy rich grace impart Long hath sin, without control, Strength to my fainting heart, Held dominion o'er my soul. My zeal inspire! As thou hast died for me, Holy Ghost, with joy divine, o may my love to thee Cheer this saddened heart of mine; Pure, warm, and changeless be, A living fire! Bid my many woes depart, Heal my wounded, bleeding heart. When ends life's transient dream, When death's cold, sullen stream Shall o'er me roll! Holy Spirit, all divine, Blest Saviour, then, in love, Dwell within this heart of mine; Fear and distrust remove; Cast down every idol-throne, O bear me safe above, Reign supreme and reign alone. A ransomed soul!
